The '''Grand Oradin Hotel''' was an upscale [[Hotel/Legends|hotel]] in [[Oradin]], [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]]. It had originally been named the '''Grand Imperial Hotel''' before Brentaal joined the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].<ref name="Revenge">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref>

